<br>
Rogue <br>
Purge Poison - This ability will remove all poison affects from the player. <br>
Purifying Tonic - Moderate Poison and Disease Cure <br>
Quick Throw - This ability will allow the player to have additional throwing attacks on one throw. <br>
Throwing Mastery - This ability will give an increased chance to critical by 5, 15, and 30 percent. <br>
Double Riposte - This ability will give the player an increase chance to execute a double riposte 10, 20, and 30 percent of the time. <br>
Poison Mastery - This ability reduces the chance of failing on an poison combinations by 10, 25, and 50 percent. Once one point is applied to this ability, the player will no longer fail in poison application. <br>
Shadow - This ability will remove the player from all hate lists. If the player is out of immediate combat, this ability will also make them invisible similar to their hide ability. <br>
Adv. Trap Negotiation - This ability will reduce the reuse times on sense and disarm traps. <br>
<br>
Monk <br>
Return Kick - This ability gives the player the chance to do a flying kick attack on ripostes in addition to the normal riposte attack. <br>
Rapid Feign - This ability reduces the players reuses time on feign death by 10, 25, and 50 percent. <br>
Chain Combo - This ability gives the player a chance to string a number of special attacks together. <br>
Purify Body - This ability removes all negative affects from their body except for fear, charm, resurrection affects. <br>
Critical Mend - This ability gives the player a chance to do a super mend 5, 10, and 25 percent of the time. <br>
Dragon Punch - This ability will give the player the ability to proc a knock back spell off of Dragon Punch. <br>
<br>
Bard <br>
Sonic Call - This gives the players song the ability to do direct damage with a stun component. <br>
Snake Charm - This ability gives the player the chance to charm an NPC as long as they have mana. The spell will follow normal level 49 charm rules. <br>
Jam Fest - Allows the player to sing their songs at a higher casting level. Note: This does not allow them tossing songs that are higher then their level. <br>
Instrument Mastery - This ability allows for specialization and improved use of all instrument types. <br>
Brass Instrument Mastery <br>
Wind Instrument Mastery <br>
Percussion Instrument Mastery <br>
Scribble Notes - This ability will reduce the amount of time it takes to memorize a song. <br>
Singing Mastery - This ability allows for specialization and improved use of the specific instrument type. <br>
Extended Notes - This ability will give the song increased ranged of 10, 15, and 25 percent. <br>
<br>
Shadowknight <br>
Enhanced Vampirism - This ability gives the player increased damage off of their self buff lifetap procs. <br>
Death Peace - This ability moves the spell Death Peace to a hotkey freeing a spell slot. <br>
Leech Touch - This ability gives the player a life tap harm touch. <br>
Super Harm Touch - This ability gives the player a low resist Harm Touch. <br>
Unholy Steed - This ability will give the player the ultimate unholy steed. <br>
<br>
Ranger <br>
Endless Quiver - This ability allows the player to shoot magical arrows that scale in damage based on skill level. <br>
Fletching/Bowyer Mastery - This ability reduces the chance of failing on an fletching combinations by 10, 25, and 50 percent. <br>
Archery Mastery - This ability gives the player to increase their archery damage from 100 to 200 percent. <br>
Dual Mastery - This ability increases the players chance to use dual wield successfully. <br>
Innate Camouflage - This ability allows the player to become invisible without the need to memorize a spell. <br>
<br>
Paladin <br>
2 Hand Bash - This ability will allow the player to bash with any 2-handed weapon. <br>
Fearless - This ability makes the player permanently immune to fear spells. <br>
Holy Steed - This ability will give the player the ultimate holy steed. <br>
Act of Valor - This ability will allow the player to transfer all of their hitpoints to a target PC. <br>
Slay Undead - This ability will turn the players crits into massive damage when fighting undead monsters. <br>
Improved Lay of Hands - This ability will turn the players Lay of Hands into a complete heal. <br>
